sequenceDiagram
  participant Buyer
  participant UI as Deal Room UI
  participant API as Backend API
  participant SM as Escrow State Machine
  participant ST as Stellar Service
  participant SC as Soroban Contract
  Buyer->>UI: Click simulate buyer deposit
  UI->>API: POST /buyer-deposit
  API->>SM: validate transition
  SM-->>API: BUYER_FUNDED or LOCKED
  API->>ST: record BuyerDeposited event
  ST->>SC: invoke deposit_buyer
  SC-->>ST: tx hash
  API-->>UI: updated deal + tx hash
